OL,3,CExeter woman to open up her home on
OL,4,CChristmas Day for people with dementia
OL,6,FWith just a few days to go until
OL,7,FChristmas, a woman from Exeter is
OL,8,Fpreparing to open up her home to
OL,9,Fpeople with dementia.Merle Weiner says
OL,10,Fshe hopes to help those who might
OL,11,Fotherwise be on their own, and give
OL,12,Ftheir carers some much-needed respite.
OL,14,F"People nowadays have families living
OL,15,Fall around the world, and it can be a
OL,16,Fvery lonely, isolated, sad time of the
OL,17,Fyear for a lot of people," Merle said.
